*Workaround:*
 1. To restore the Space Directory view: Delete cache cookies for the site.
- Firefox: Tools (or History) -> Clear Recent History -> Cookies when Time range is "Everything"
- Chrome: chrome://settings/ -> Show advanced settings... -> (Privacy) Content settings -> All cookies and site data -> (search for the site) -> Remove all (or specifically the 'Local storage' cookie)

 2. To avoid it from happening again: Remove the special characters from the each Space Categories.

